8. A method according to claim 7 wherein:
(a) said step of squeezing includes squeezing the jacket material between first and second opposing clamp members;
(i) the first clamp member having a first plurality of peaks and valleys;
(ii) the second clamp member having a second plurality of peaks and valleys;
(A) the second plurality of peaks sized and arranged to mateably engage the first plurality of valleys; and
(B) the second plurality of valleys sized and arranged to mateably engage the first plurality of peaks.
